Sotillion, the Summer Queen, is a goddess of summer, comfort, ease, and the South Wind, a daughter of the primal storm-deity Procan. She is a lesser deity of Oeridian origin, Chaotic Good with Chaotic Neutral tendencies. She is married to Zilchus, the god of wealth.
Her Realm on Ysgard's first Layer is called the Green Fields. She is also sometimes found in Grandfather Oak in Arvandor.
Sources: Dragon magazine #264 - "The Oeridian Lesser Gods",
